                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-66-off380 t18080217-66-cd381"></join>, two bags, value 1 s. sixty pound weight of vermilion, value 13 l. two sticks of distilled verdigrease, value 2 l. eleven pound weight of bronze, value 7 l. 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18080217-66-victim593" type="victimName">
