                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-66-defend589 t18080217-66-punish387"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 30.</p>
               <p>HICKEY, <rs id="t18080217-66-verdict388" type="verdictDescription">
